{
  "stem": "6966.6",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So days go by.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I see the doctor in my ward.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But before, before that, yes, I'm laying in still in the ward with the rotten feet, and they tell me, tomorrow morning you're going out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Your, your temperature's gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Tomorrow morning, you're going out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Oh, gosh, now I've got to go out in the cold-- snow, cold.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that same-- same afternoon, and in the evening, I get a pain in my ear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm laying there in bed, and there's one man-- non-Jew-- who looks after the sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And every evening, they take up your temperature with thermomet-- thermometer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there is another thing that somewhat happened to me in the other-- in the other sick barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he comes to me, and he looks, and he says, you've got a temperature.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What's wrong?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I says, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I've got pains in the ear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So he looks at it, he says, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I had erysipelas, erysipelas-- contagious.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So the next morning, the doctor put a wooden-- a crepe paper on my foot, and boy, that was ugly, dirty.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And on a little barrow, I was taken to another barrack.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And as I get into the barrack, I sits down on a wooden bench.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the doctor there-- I think it was a Russian doctor-- and he looks at my feet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The bandage was gone already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he, he looks at me and looks at my ear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And then I must have said a few English words because he calls out to another doctor there, and the other doctor is Albert Kongs.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Albert Kongs, he was on the resistance in Belgium, if he can hear me.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
